106
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,930
So why is he going up to the patient's ward?

107
00:08:58,930 --> 00:09:01,130
Calm down, Go Yoo!

108
00:09:02,970 --> 00:09:04,650
Gosh...

109
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,310
I knew it.

110
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:37,670
You study like a hard laborer. How could your body stand it?

111
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:38,990
I'm not the only one.

112
00:09:38,990 --> 00:09:42,990
You idiot! You have no excuses.

113
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:46,270
We're all screwed.

114
00:09:57,700 --> 00:09:59,600
Stand up and walk.

115
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:02,040
Are you already acting like a patient?

116
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:35,760
Joon Hee is very sick, so he won't be able to come to school for the time being.

117
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,200
Everyone should send him a text of encouragement.

118
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,900
 Yes. 

119
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:43,390
Soon Tak, you should let everyone know his phone number.

120
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:45,320
Okay...

121
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:48,540
Did Go Yoo go on training, or did he go home early?

122
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:51,010
Training...

123
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:54,010
That punk. He didn't even let me know... Study hard.

124
00:10:54,010 --> 00:10:56,100
 Goodbye. 

125
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:58,190
 Didn't you say you were going to ask me something? 

126
00:10:58,190 --> 00:11:00,360
 I know that one. 

127
00:11:13,300 --> 00:11:14,280
Yeah?

128
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,900
Could you give these gym clothes back to Go Yoo?

129
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:20,580
I'm going to the hospital today.

130
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:25,080
Do you want to go with me?

131
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,870
Is that funny?

132
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:31,710
Go Yoo is there.

133
00:11:33,050 --> 00:11:35,000
No.

134
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,760
Then I'll give it to him.

135
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:40,460
Yeah.

136
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:44,120
Is Go Joon Hee very sick?

137
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,600
   

138
00:11:54,170 --> 00:11:56,490
Aren't you tired?

139
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,860
