140
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:05,240
- What about you? 
 - Why would I be tired?

141
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:21,510
I explained everything. Stop giving me the eye and leave.

142
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:25,820
I'm not giving you the eye, but I feel like your plan is too casual.

143
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:28,770
We have a tragic history!

144
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:33,530
There isn't anyone who can give him a kidney.

145
00:12:33,530 --> 00:12:35,330
Unless we do a transplant from a living donor,

146
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:39,580
we can keep him on dialysis while waiting for a brain-dead patient donor.

147
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,120
Gosh!

148
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:02,860
Soon Tak, are you sick? Your face is pale!

149
